title: Braised Potato Recipe
description: Braised Potato Recipe | Quick and Easy Potato Recipes | Easy Vegan Recipes
text: 5 - 6 kilos Medium Potatoes - 2 Tablespoon Oil  (Olive oil preferably) - 3 - 4 Garlic (roughly chopped) - Salt to Taste - 1 Cup Tomato Paste (strained tomatoes) OR Tomato puree - 1 Teaspoon dry oregano  OR  2 Tablespoon fresh oregano - 2 Tablespoon fresh Thyme (OPTIONAL) - 1/4 Teaspoon Cayenne pepper (OPTIONAL) - 1 + 1/2 Cup water
